method.name: IsInitialized
method.comment: Tests whether the object has been initialized.

method.name: _gethasgesture
method.comment: Gets whether a gesture (such as a click) was associated with the request. Added in API level 21.

method.name: _getisformainframe
method.comment: Gets whether the request was made in order to fetch the main frame's document. Added in API level 21.

method.name: _getisredirect
method.comment: Gets whether the request was a result of a server-side redirect. Added in API level 24.

method.name: _getmethod
method.comment: Gets the method associated with the request, for example "GET". Added in API level 21.

method.name: _getrequestheaders
method.comment: Gets the headers associated with the request. Added in API level 21.

method.name: _geturl
method.comment: Gets the URL for which the resource request was made. Added in API level 21.

method.name: _initialize
method.comment: Initializes the object. Pass android.webkit.WebResourceRequest from inline Java code to initialize new instance. Added in API level 21.

method.name: _toobject
method.comment: Returns Object as android.webkit.WebResourceRequest which can be used in Java Code. Added in API level 21.
